---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Surveys & Maps"
	description="Course surveying and drainage mapping to give golf courses an accurate, permanent record for targeted maintenance and investment decisions."
>
	<section class="section section--tight hero">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="eyebrow">Services · Surveys &amp; Maps</span>
			<h1>Know exactly what's under your course</h1>
			<p class="lede">
				Many courses have incomplete or out-of-date records of their own drainage networks. A
				proper survey turns guesswork into a plan, and a permanent reference for every
				maintenance decision that follows.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="grid grid--2">
				<div class="card">
					<h3>What's covered</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Topographic and drainage surveys</li>
						<li>Mapping of existing pipe runs, outfalls, and catch basins</li>
						<li>Course maps for maintenance planning and future works</li>
						<li>Baseline records to measure the impact of new drainage work</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<img
					src="/images/surveys-maps.jpg"
					alt="Aerial survey map of a golf course with contour lines and drainage layout overlaid"
					style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px;"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section--alt">
		<div class="container" style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1.5rem; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;">
			<div>
				<h2 style="margin-top:0;">Start with a survey</h2>
				<p style="margin-bottom:0; max-width:34rem;">
					A clear map of your existing drainage is usually the first step before any new works
					are planned, get in touch to discuss scope.
				</p>
			</div>
			<a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact/">Get in touch</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
